654
00:59:06,690 --> 00:59:07,889
Quer uma bebida?

655
00:59:07,890 --> 00:59:09,490
Sim.

656
00:59:24,790 --> 00:59:26,390
Gosta deles?

657
00:59:26,690 --> 00:59:29,589
